title: Reports of active shooter at Florida high school
text:
Reports of active shooter at Florida high school Wednesday, February 14, 2018 - 01:05 
Deputies in Broward County, Florida, were responding on Wednesday to reports of an active shooter at a high school in the town of Parkland, a spokeswoman for the sheriff's department said. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
